\v 3 ns…õe w ºaho…îden w…î mmaa\f + \fr 31.3 \ft Saa mmaa yi y…õ mmaa adwamanfo…î a w…îw…î ahemfie a w…îb…õtumi atwe …îhene adwene afiri n ºadwuma so.\f* ho, 
\q2 w…în a w…îgu ahemfo asu no. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 4 Lemuel, ns√£ ny…õ mma ahemfo; 
\q2 asanom ny…õ mma ahemfo, 
\q2 …õns…õ s…õ sodifo…î pere nsaden ho; 
